    {
      "id": "39",
      "name": "推薦角色",
      "components": [
        {
          "component_id": "customize",
          "data": {
            "data": {
              "parsed_content": [
                {
                  "alignment": "center",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "amount": 1,
                      "display_style": "card",
                      "ep_id": 51,
                      "icon_url": "https://bbs.hoyolab.com/hoyowiki/picture/character/Xiao_icon.png",
                      "menu_id": 2,
                      "name": "魈",
                      "type": "custom_entry"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "color:#ffffff"
                      ],
                      "text": "魈自身為璃月的角色，至少可獲得一層特效；同時，魈常與鍾離搭配獲得護盾和減抗效果、與雲堇搭配獲得傷害提升，可以比較有效地利用這一武器的特效。",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "alignment": "center",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "amount": 1,
                      "display_style": "card",
                      "ep_id": 46,
                      "icon_url": "https://bbs.hoyolab.com/hoyowiki/picture/character/Zhongli_icon.png",
                      "menu_id": 2,
                      "name": "鍾離",
                      "type": "custom_entry"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "color:#ffffff"
                      ],
                      "text": "鍾離自身為璃月角色，需要鍾離補充輸出時可考慮該武器。",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "alignment": "center",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "amount": 1,
                      "display_style": "card",
                      "ep_id": 29,
                      "icon_url": "https://bbs.hoyolab.com/hoyowiki/picture/character/Shenhe_icon.png",
                      "menu_id": 2,
                      "name": "申鶴",
                      "type": "custom_entry"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "color:#ffffff"
                      ],
                      "text": "申鶴自身作為璃月角色，可附帶一層武器特效；且因申鶴與甘雨/重雲的搭配較為常見，該武器大部分情況下有2~3層特效，作為四星武器中白值第二高且特效也增加",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "bold",
                        "color:#ffe14b"
                      ],
                      "text": "攻擊力",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "color:#ffffff"
                      ],
                      "text": "的武器，是申鶴四星武器的優選武器之一。",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "alignment": "center",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "amount": 1,
                      "display_style": "card",
                      "ep_id": 50,
                      "icon_url": "https://bbs.hoyolab.com/hoyowiki/picture/character/Xiangling_icon.png",
                      "menu_id": 2,
                      "name": "香菱",
                      "type": "custom_entry"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "color:#ffffff"
                      ],
                      "text": "香菱自身為璃月角色，至少可獲得一層特效。香菱常與行秋搭配，多數情況下都能至少獲得兩層特效。但使用該武器時需要注意保證香菱的元素充能效率充足以維持其元素爆發的釋放頻率。",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                }
              ]
            }
          }
        }
      ]
    }
